&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Salaried GP vacancy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking to work as a part time Salaried GP in Hull then this is a great opportunity for you. We are a small, friendly, family orientated GMS practice located close to Beverley and the beautiful Yorkshire Wolds and Coastline. We pride ourselves on providing excellent care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To support our Practice we have a home visiting service staffed by urgent care practitioners and a long term conditions nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We were rated Hull’s top GP Practice for patient satisfaction in 2018 and have a 5 star rating on NHS choices; we also have a GOOD CQC rating.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for compassionate and motivated GPs to join us. If you feel you are ready for a change or new challenge then please read on and apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
